  <brief_title>Endoscopic Evaluation of Upper Gastrointestinal (GI) Mucosal Damage Induced by PL-2200 Versus Aspirin in Healthy Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Single-Blind, Endoscopic Evaluation Of Upper GI Mucosal Damage Induced By PL-2200 Versus Aspirin In Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
