  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the gastrointestinal safety of PL-2200 versus immediate-release aspirin by
      assessing endoscopic gastroduodenal mucosal injury at approved daily cardiac-protective doses
      of aspirin (325 mg) in normal healthy volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
